<p>
  <img class="headshot" src="/images/static/staff/tim.jpg" alt="Tim Caswell" />
  <b>Tim Caswell</b> joined DocumentCloud in January as a JavaScript/Ruby Developer.    
  Some of his notable open-source projects include the 
  <a href="http://github.com/creationix/haml-js">JavaScript version of HAML</a>, 
